description: His life in cybercrime began at age 11, investigators say, and went on to incursions into Nvidia and “Grand Theft Auto.” His case has brought worries about a new breed of fearless young hackers.
title: This Teenage Hacker Became a Legend Attacking Companies. Then His Rivals Attacked Him.

description: SoftBank Group Chief Executive Masayoshi Son said he believed artificial general intelligence, in which computers have human-level cognitive abilities, would be achieved in two to three years.
title: SoftBank's Son Says Artificial General Intelligence to Be Achieved in a Few Years
